Volite *volite* li ples? (Do you like dancing?)
Oni *volite* da čitaju knjige. (They like to read books.)
Oni *volite* da jedu sladoled. (They like to eat ice cream.)
Ona *voli* da putuje. (She likes to travel.)
Mi *volimo* da igramo fudbal. (We like to play football.)
On *voli* da ide na more. (He likes to go to the sea.)
Ona *voli* da sluša muziku. (She likes to listen to music.)